## Dependencies

- [Stimulus](https://stimulus.hotwired.dev/)

## Installation

Add polaris_view_components to your Gemfile:

```bash
bundle add polaris_view_components
```

Run installer:

```bash
bin/rails polaris_view_components:install
```

